com.nutiteq.components
Class Components

java.lang.Object
  com.nutiteq.components.Components

public class Components
extends java.lang.Object

Components is a container for internal state of the map view. It contains layers, caches, etc. This state should be retained when activity is recreated within application.

Field Summary
